q-answer\">Yes, we require a $100 deposit with the signed contract to reserve your booth for your event date. Your final payment is required two weeks before the date of your event.</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-question\">What methods of payment are available?</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">Right now we only accept cash, checks and PayPal.  Contact us for more details.</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-question\">What if I have to cancel or reschedule my event?</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">We will work with you to reschedule your photo booth rental upon availability.</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-question\">Will there be someone at the event to make sure everything runs smoothly?</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">We will be there to set up the photo booth before your events starts, and will remain on hand throughout your event to make sure everyone is having a great time and that the photobooth stays stocked and running smoothly.</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-question\">Can we customize the printout design?</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">Certainly! We highly suggest that you work with us to customize background and text that is displayed on your prints. Whether you want to use a logo, names and dates, or your favorite quote, we will do everything that we can to make it happen. Virtually anything is possible with the customization level of our prints.</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-question\">Do we need any special kind of hookup or facilities, to set up the photobooth on-site?</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">A normal AC power source is all that is needed, preferably within 10-20 feet.</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-question\">Can we get a copy of the images taken by the digital photobooth on a disk?</div>\r\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">Yes all photobooth rentals include a CD or DVD of all the photos taken at high resolution.</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq-footer\">For any additional questions please call us at 703.898.1702 or <a href=\"/contact\">send us a message!</a> </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>','FAQs','','publish','open','closed','','faqs','','','2012-02-23 22:19:14','2012-02-23 22:19:14','',0,'http://test.dc-photobooth.com:8085/?page_id=33',5,'page','',0),(34,1,'2012-01-15 01:43:00','2012-01-15 01:43:00','','Accessories','','inherit','open','open','','33-revision','','','2012-01-15 01:43:00','2012-01-15 01:43:00','',33,'http://test.dc-photobooth.com:8085/33-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(35,1,'2012-01-15 01:43:05','2012-01-15 01:43:05',' ','','','publish','open','open','','35','','','2012-01-15 01:43:05','2012-01-15 01:43:05','',0,'http://test.dc-photobooth.com:8085/35/',5,'nav_menu_item','',0),(41,1,'2012-01-15 02:18:44','2012-01-15 02:18:44','','Blog','','publish','open','closed','','blog','','','2012-01-18 04:53:18','2012-01-18 04:53:18','',0,'http://test.dc-photobooth.com:8085/?page_id=41',6,'page','',0),(42,1,'2012-01-15 01:58:32','2012-01-15 01:58:32','','Blog','','inherit','open','open','','41-revision','','','2012-01-15 01:58:32','2012-01-15 01:58:32','',41,'http://test.dc-photobooth.com:8085/41-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(43,1,'2012-01-15 02:18:44','2012-01-15 02:18:44',' ','','','publish','open','open','','43','','','2012-01-15 02:18:44','2012-01-15 02:18:44','',0,'http://test.dc-photobooth.com:8085/43/',5,'nav_menu_item','',0),(44,1,'2012-01-15 02:18:44','2012-01-15 02:18:44','','Blog','','inherit','open','open','','41-revision-2','','','2012-01-15 02:18:44','2012-01-15 02:18:44','',41,'http://test.dc-photobooth.com:8085/41-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0),(38,1,'2012-01-15 01:40:21','2012-01-15 01:40:21','','Rates','','inherit','open','open','','28-revision-4','','','2012-01-15 01:40:21','2012-01-15 01:40:21','',28,'http://test.dc-photobooth.com:8085/28-revision-4/',0,'revision','',0),(39,1,'2012-01-13 04:10:42','2012-01-13 04:10:42','Sample page!','Contact Us','','inherit','open','open','','9-revision-3','','','2012-01-13 04:10:42','2012-01-13 04:10:42','',9,'http://test.dc-photobooth.com:8085/9-revis